{"type": "article", "id": 27921, "title": "可以拉伸的烛台", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-08T07:24:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142502yr1PHjduqQpf2RIc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>德国的 inbetween 工作室最近推出了一系列<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/37747837/Brass-pop-up-candle-holder-by-studio-inbetween\">黄铜制的烛台</a>，可以说真的是把烛台都“玩出了花”。乍看上去它就是一个普通的金属片，从包装中取出时很像是一张老式唱片，表面还有着年轮一样的镂空图案。你可以根据自己的需要将它拉开，将蜡烛放在底部，小巧又不失精致，和玻璃杯搭配使用的效果也颇有情调。这是它的<a href=\"http://storeinbetween.tictail.com/\">购买链接</a>，售价为 13 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142456PmhfQiYI2K7xB10C.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.67366212\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021424575pFy14h8cK0VEQtY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142500adD1PnkOLKeJfFtU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142500ti6wVxRNsBrykA8q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}